{"tid":768591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人生要幾多層樓］點為止盡孝道？","createTime":"2018-08-05T13:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T03:08:59.000Z","uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e045c27ebf2104bf58396d5f30ee4ba21ea459b2","tid":768591,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"屋企人喺灣仔租緊樓<br />\n阿媽有間九龍單人豪宅揸喺手供緊（有日後會斷供嘅可能性）<br />\n<br />\n自己21歲 諗緊將來<br />\n放假返香港 阿媽問我諗日後點<br />\n<br />\n我答：<br />\n首先買間南豐新邨兩房（600呎）嘅屋俾阿爸阿媽先 兩個人鬧交都可以分房安心瞓<br />\n最差打算係阿媽揀離婚 阿爸都唔會生活得太差 （未計housing price inflation 宜家800萬）<br />\n之後再買間細嘅一兩房（400呎）俾阿婆阿爺 宜家兩個老人喺大陸住 返嚟香港都係要痴喺父母度瞓（都係兩房細單位），日後買個樓俾佢地 返大陸拎去自租又好 留喺度自住又好 起碼佢地都可以安享下生活 話曬宜家先70歲仲未有得快死住 第時有間屋病痛都少啲（300-600萬 睇地區）<br />\n<br />\n跟住買間樓自住 300萬樓下啦 住唐樓自己都冇乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n跟住再留筆錢第時結婚生仔後買間大啲嘅層<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但都冇乜可能了<br />\n因為幫父母同兩老買家都應該40尾、50幾歲 邊仲有活力同時間搞咁多嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4255bb8a3f8300a54abda2e26b5e379f2eb1330","tid":768591,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"結論 <br />\n25歲出嚟做嘢 用30年賺2000萬買三間房再留少少做backup/upgrade <br />\n55歲方能功德圓滿 為父母添衣為家庭謀福<br />\n<br />\n平均一個月賺六萬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7c645d8a6b8053f8d846dbee0b1f3bbbe9d892","tid":768591,"uid":119502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"有時間就做左暑期作業先啦同學"},{"pid":"bce674ce23adf43c87055c885ef5738d9c641ab3","tid":768591,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7c645d8a6b8053f8d846dbee0b1f3bbbe9d892","tid":768591,"uid":119502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"有時間就做左暑期作業先啦同學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"For discussion jer."},{"pid":"4a92f2545f82be1f6df7ee7d2ffe23b505a6375b","tid":768591,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"做晒暑假功課未"},{"pid":"f0d00b51d6357fc3911bca4aa2028fbee5037ed6","tid":768591,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7c645d8a6b8053f8d846dbee0b1f3bbbe9d892","tid":768591,"uid":119502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"有時間就做左暑期作業先啦同學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc82dd85fe041b38225301543daafd78e1e6b41","tid":768591,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a92f2545f82be1f6df7ee7d2ffe23b505a6375b","tid":768591,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"做晒暑假功課未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46dc686c3c655f9a7313bf900e0904f9739f1b5","tid":768591,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"其實有樣嘢係認真嘅<br />\n<br />\n就係點都會幫長輩買層樓 再輪到自己<br />\n即係好可能到時自己都唔會有樓"}]}